text.tspan: O my God, within Thee there is eternal life
O behold, from the throne of our God and the Lamb
Flows a river of water of life
God the source, Christ the fount, God the Spirit the flow,
Springing up as a river of life.
Jesus Lord, from my spirit I turn unto Thee
Open wide, call Thy name, drink Thee in;
Dearest Lord, to this stream I outpour utterly;
Triune God, flow as life, flood my being.
